Message:
Catherine,

We would like to personally thank you for your amazing commitment, creativity and hard work throughout this year. To express our sincere appreciation this holiday season, we are gifting you this special GCode reward. You can instantly redeem it and shop our rewards store: just click on the Add to Wallet button below to go to a website to create an account.

Wishing you a happy and healthy holiday season and a successful New Year!

P.S. You can shop with this secure GCode for 365 days, but it needs to be activated in the next 90 days.
